    <item>
      <title>罢工导致美国东海岸、墨西哥湾港口关闭，危及经济</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-01/us-dockworkers-strike-set-to-go-ahead-after-no-deal-announced-m1pwyo3k</link>
      <description><![CDATA[码头工人已走出美国东部和墨西哥湾沿岸的所有主要港口，标志着罢工的开始，此次罢工可能波及全球最大经济体，并在总统大选前几周引发政治动荡。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-01/us-dockworkers-strike-set-to-go-ahead-after-no-deal-announced-m1pwyo3k</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 01 Oct 2024 04:03:31 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>瑞典房东以三年来最快的速度出售债券</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-01/swedish-landlords-sell-bonds-at-the-fastest-pace-in-three-years</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于利率下降推动债券发行量激增，瑞典房东重返债券市场的数量达到了 2021 年繁荣时期以来的最高水平。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-01/swedish-landlords-sell-bonds-at-the-fastest-pace-in-three-years</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 01 Oct 2024 04:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>伯克希尔计划发行新日元债券以提振贸易公司</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-01/berkshire-plans-second-yen-bond-sale-in-2024-picks-underwriters</link>
      <description><![CDATA[沃伦·巴菲特旗下的伯克希尔哈撒韦公司计划今年第二次发行日元债券，因市场猜测该公司希望增加在日本的投资，这推动了贸易公司的股价上涨。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-01/berkshire-plans-second-yen-bond-sale-in-2024-picks-underwriters</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 01 Oct 2024 01:04:36 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中东紧张局势与利比亚供应前景不符，油价持稳</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-30/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-oct-1</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于中东地缘政治风险（以色列开始对黎巴嫩境内进行地面袭击）与利比亚恢复供应的前景相冲突，油价在第四季度初趋于稳定。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-30/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-oct-1</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 30 Sep 2024 23:26:51 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
